8. Information Fusion Engine

This is one of the most important parts of the system.

Inputs come from different modalities:

Voice

Image

Text

Location

Metadata

The Fusion Engine creates a single canonical representation:

{
  "issue": "...",
  "location": "...",
  "category": "...",
  "citizenIntent": "...",
  "evidence": [...]
}

Every downstream AI module consumes this unified object rather than raw inputs.

