10. Structured Output Contract

Every AI module must return structured JSON.

Example:

{
  "summary": "Streetlights are not functioning near MG Road.",

  "category": "Electricity",

  "themes": [
    "Street Lighting",
    "Road Safety"
  ],

  "confidence": 0.93
}

Avoid free-form text whenever possible.

11. AI Analysis Model

Persist results separately from raw submissions.

analysis/

    analysisId

        submissionId

        language

        translatedText

        summary

        category

        themes

        sentiment

        duplicateCluster

        hotspot

